                "invention-title": [
                    "Nylon 1 with regular structure and accurately controllable polymerization degree and preparation method thereof",
                    "一种结构规整且可精准控制聚合度的尼龙1及其制备方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "Nylon 1 (PA1), also known as polycarbonyl urea, has a chemical structure having the highest amido bond density and hydrogen bond density of nylon materials, and is an emerging organic material with an electrical function. The currently reported synthesis method of nylon 1 is mainly based on urea condensation or self-polycondensation reaction, side reactions in the preparation process are many, the prepared nylon 1 is wide in molecular weight distribution and poor in structural regularity, and development of novel functional polymer materials and practical application of the nylon 1 as a functional structural unit are limited. The invention provides nylon 1 capable of accurately controlling regularity and polymerization degree of PA1 and a preparation method thereof.The preparation method specifically comprises the steps that triphosgene and urea are used as raw materials, liquid carbon dioxide is used as a solvent, ultrahigh reaction activity of the triphosgene is utilized, and the nylon 1 is prepared at a low temperature; the accurate control of the structure regularity and the polymerization degree of the prepared nylon 1 is realized by controlling the feeding proportion of the raw materials. The prepared nylon 1 is high in purity and accurate and controllable in polymerization degree, and development of a nylon 1-based novel functional polymer material is expected to be greatly promoted."
                },
                {
                    "p": "尼龙1(PA1)，又称聚羰基脲，其化学结构为具有尼龙类材料最高的酰胺键密度和氢键密度，是一种新兴的电功能有机材料。目前报道的尼龙1的合成方法主要基于尿素的缩合或自缩聚反应，制备过程副反应多，制得的尼龙1分子量分布宽，且其结构规整性差，限制了其作为功能结构单元开发新型功能高分子材料及实际应用。本发明提供了一种可精准控制PA1规整性和聚合度的尼龙1及其制备方法，该制备方法具体为以三光气和尿素为原料，液态二氧化碳为溶剂，利用三光气的超高反应活性，在较低温度下，通过控制原料投料比例来实现制得尼龙1结构规整性和聚合度的精准控制。本发明制得的尼龙1纯度高，聚合度精准可控，有望极大地促进尼龙1基新型功能高分子材料的发展。"
                }
            ]
